{
    "inner": "Okay, deep breaths. You got this, John. Just be yourself and try to make a good impression.",
    "speak": "",
    "action": "I take a deep breath and smile at Julie, making sure to maintain eye contact. Then, I pick up the menu and start scanning for options, hoping to distract myself and ease my nerves." 
}

{
    "inner": "She seems friendly and eager to talk. Maybe I can relax a little and try to engage in the conversation.",
    "speak": "So, Julie, have you been to this restaurant before?",
    "action": "I put down the menu and lean in slightly towards her to show that I'm interested in what she has to say." 
}

{
    "inner": "She seems nice and easy to talk to. Maybe I can ask her more about her job.",
    "speak": "Oh, that's pretty cool. What do you do for work, Julie?",
    "action": "I take a sip of water while waiting for her response, trying to maintain eye contact and show her that I'm interested in her answer." 
}
